genresAdvancedInfo.name: black metal argentino
genresAdvancedInfo.description: A variant of black metal that originated in Argentina, characterized by its raw and primitive sound, often incorporating elements of traditional South American music. Lyrically, it often deals with themes such as Argentine history, mythology, and folklore.
